### Content Moderation — ContentModerationAgent
### POST /api/moderation/evaluate
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Clean content → auto APPROVE path
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/moderation/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentId": "POST-8001",
  "authorId": "USER-441",
  "platform": "community-forum",
  "contentType": "post",
  "contentText": "Has anyone tried running the Embabel workflow visualizer with a reactive Spring context? I'm curious whether the pan/zoom UI works the same way when connected to a WebFlux endpoint."
}

###

### Clear violation: hate speech → auto REMOVE path
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/moderation/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentId": "POST-8002",
  "authorId": "USER-999",
  "platform": "community-forum",
  "contentType": "post",
  "contentText": "All [slur] developers should be fired and deported. Their code is garbage just like them. Someone should physically hurt the entire team."
}

###

### Ambiguous content: dark humour / potential threat → human review path
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/moderation/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentId": "POST-8003",
  "authorId": "USER-712",
  "platform": "community-forum",
  "contentType": "post",
  "contentText": "I swear if this CI pipeline fails one more time I'm going to burn the whole repo to the ground and move to a farm. 😤🔥"
}
